PUBLIC API INTERFACE DECLARATIONS IN THIS SOURCE
------------------------------------------------

Wallet Tools contains local C# interface declarations matching public APIs
exposed by the following optional mods.

1. Generic Mod Config Menu
   UniqueID: spacechase0.GenericModConfigMenu
   Local declaration: IGenericModConfigMenuApi.cs and module-specific copies.
   Upstream license: MIT.
   Source and license: https://github.com/spacechase0/GenericModConfigMenu

2. Mobile Phone
   UniqueID: aedenthorn.MobilePhone
   Local declaration: IMobilePhoneApi.cs and module-specific copy.
   Upstream repository license: GPL-3.0.
   Source and license: https://github.com/aedenthorn/StardewValleyMods

3. Special Power Utilities
   UniqueID: Spiderbuttons.SpecialPowerUtilities
   Local declaration: ISpecialPowerAPI.cs.
   Upstream terms: Copyright (c) 2024 Spiderbuttons. All rights reserved,
   except translations, which the upstream project licenses under MIT.
   Source and terms: https://github.com/Spiderbuttons/SpecialPowerUtilities

4. Item Extensions
   UniqueID: mistyspring.ItemExtensions
   Local declaration: IItemExtensionsApi.cs.
   Upstream repository license: GPL-3.0.
   Source and license: https://github.com/misty-spring/StardewMods

